All in one tuition Center teachers are fun and lively. I have English and POA tuition which both helped me improve a lot. Used to have math but after a year I felt confident enough to stop.

My son has been attending English classes at RG Channel Future School since beginning of this year. He looks forward to his lesson every week and I have seen an improvement in his English grades. He also attended RG's June holiday programs where he got to illustrate and create his own story. He had a lot of fun and has requested to attend the upcoming Dec holiday program. :) I am very happy with what RG Channel Future School has offered, in terms of providing a very nurturing learning environment as well as the academic support provided to my son. I will highly recommend the school to other parents.

If you live in east, you should definitely let your kid try out this center. Top down left right they are very student centric. Management, teachers and staff are very helpful. Fee is very reasonable that i feel sorry as they are really very dedicated in helping the student! My elder kid stay with them for about 6 years and younger 4 years n still counting. Thank youðŸ¥°

Wonderful & caring staff & teachers. Very conducive for learning with good supporting learning facilities. Teachers are very experienced & provided motivation & guidance towards exam excellence! My kid got into RI with very good PSLE (2019) result! Thks RG!
